  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "The preset Oskar Sala reached for when the director wanted alien and uncanny. Odd divisions only — ÷3, ÷5, ÷7. bodyFreq 62 Hz (≈B♭1), deliberately between pitch classes. morphGlide 0.85: each note slides into its own undoing. This is the sound from the seance scripture: 'the serpent does not play notes, it changes shape between them.'",
